{"title": "File Listing", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "ftp-protocol/file-listing", "html": "<h1 id=\"file-listing\">File Listing</h1>\n<h2 id=\"listing-files\">Listing Files</h2>\n<p>Directory listings using the <code>--ls</code> flag, which includes file permissions:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc ftp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u 'marshall' -p 'badpassword' --ls</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>ftp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;marshall&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">&#39;badpassword&#39;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>--ls\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Banner:<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>vsFTPd<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3</span>.0.5<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>marshall:badpassword\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><span class=\"m\">21</span><span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">    </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Directory<span class=\"w\"> </span>Listing\nFTP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.0.10<span class=\"w\">   </span><spa